A \star \mathrm{d}x
A \star  \mathrm{d}x \star \mathrm{d}x 
 \int_{0}^{t} \int_{0} ^{t-\tau} A(t-\tau-s) \mathrm{d}x(s) \mathrm{d}x(\tau)
t-\tau = w
\dot x\ast \dot x 
dx\star dx
A\star dx\star dx = A\ast \dot x \ast \dot x = A\ast (\dot x \ast \dot x)
\int_0^t A(t-u) \int_0^u \dot x(u-s)\dot x(s)\,ds\,du.
\int_0^t A(t-u) \int_0^u \dot x(u-s)\,dx(s)\,du.
x^t(w)=x(t-w)
t-\tau=w
dx^t(w)=-dx(t-w)
\int_0^t \int_0^{t-\tau} A(t-\tau-s)\,dx(s)\,dx(\tau)=\int_0^t \int_0^{w} A(w-s)\,dx(s)\,dx^t(w)
